Liteapi,org,is,a,crypto,currency,facilitator,that,provides,resources,to,utilize,or,incorporate,litecoin,payment,into,merchant,applications,The,Liteapi,org,API,allows,users,to,receive,payments,get,exchange,rates,access,the,blockchain,and,make,other,calls,The,API,also,allows,users,to,build,apps,that,utilize,litecoin,or,add,litecoin,functionality,to,existing,applications,The,API,uses,REST,calls,returns,JSON,and,uses,SSL,for,authentication